rows.label: qev092506_MSG0001
rows.name:
How goes the mission? Are you finding the materials
for the Skell flight module all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0002
rows.name:
If you're stuck, I can share the intel Tatsu scrounged up.
So what do you need help with?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Lin about the upgraded coil part.

rows.label: qev092506_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Lin about the light-speed jet fin.

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0003
rows.name:
Tatsu said you could get those from oc-servs,
the Ganglion weapons patrolling the bridge in the
Southern Cinderdunes of Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0004
rows.name:
...Then he said he'd leave the rest to you and ran off
like a massive chicken.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0005
rows.name: Useless when it really countsâ€”that's our Tatsu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0006
rows.name:
Tatsu said you could get one from aetrygons,
the piscinoid indigens around Oblivia's King's Falls.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0007
rows.name: So at least he got you a location, I guess?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0008
rows.name:
But as soon as he heard aetrygons were ferocious
carnivores, he started making excuses about not
wanting to get involved any deeper.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0009
rows.name:
I'm sure he's napping or goofing off about now.
Honestly, he's hopeless.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0010
rows.name:
I've double-checked and triple-checked up to the very
last minute. I can guarantee nothing's hooked up
backward this time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092506_MSG0011
rows.name:
You're set to make a beeline for the wild blue yonder.
Time to take flight![ST:wait ]
